title: The Wire - Commentaries for Season 1-4 (Audio only)
description:
All DVD commentary tracks for Season 1-4.

Encoded with: lame3.97 -V5 --vbr-new (~80-110kbit)

To save bandwidth, there is no video, since most likely you already have original episodes or can get them easily. You can mux this audio to your files with Avi-Mux GUI or some other tool. Or use a player that supports loading external audio tracks. Or start playing it in audio player while video is running.
